extends ../layout/base

block variables

    - var title='';
    - var description='';
    - var pageClass='affiliate';

block content
    section.section.section--inner-top-two
        .container.container--inner-top
            .inner-top.inner-top--secondary
                .inner-top__left
                    .title.title--section-small.title--white
                    .title.title--large.title--white How
                        span.default-gradient  It Works
                    .simple-text.simple-text--medium-two.simple-text--white
                        p Our evaluation process is your opportunity to showcase your trading skills and earn significant profits with our capital.
                        p  We identify talented traders who exhibit discipline, focus, and consistent profitability in financial markets. Learn more about our evaluation process and start your journey towards success as a trader with our company.
                    a.button.button--medium.button--gradient-bg.button--shadow
                        .button__text Get Started
                .inner-top__pic
                    img(src='content/images/empty.gif' class="lazy" data-src="content/images/pics/work.png" width="675" height="675" alt="notebook")
                    img(src='content/images/empty.gif' class="lazy" data-src="content/images/pics/work.png" width="675" height="675" alt="notebook")
    section.section.section--steps.js-inview
        .container
            .steps-block
                .steps-block__top-title
                    .title.title--border-mini
                        span Step One
                .steps-block__top
                    h2.title.title--section
                        | Choose A
                        span.default-gradient  Funded Forex Plan
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                        | We want to provide our traders with a comfortable trading environment. That’s why we have come up with three different models. In all the models, even from your assessment phase, you will earn a 15% profit as a reward for your performance.We recommend you to go through both the models and pick a package that suits your trading style
                .steps-block__list
                    .step-item.border-gradient
                        .step-item__body
                            .simple-text.simple-text--bold.simple-text--medium.default-gradient Evaluation
                            .title.title--medium.title--white One Step
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium-two
                                | Your goal in this model will be to prove your trading ability in 2 phases with very realistic profit targets. Once you achieve the targets, you will start trading on FundedNext Account with a 80% profit split. The profit split percentage can be increased all the way up to 90% based on your performance.
                            a(href="#").button.button--gradient-border.button--small.border-gradient
                                .button__text Learn More
                    .step-item.border-gradient
                        .step-item__body
                            .simple-text.simple-text--bold.simple-text--medium.default-gradient Evaluation
                            .title.title--medium.title--white Two Step
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium-two
                                | Your goal in this model will be to hit an ambitious profit target with no time limit. Once you achieve the target, you will start trading on FundedNext Account with a 60% profit split. The profit split percentage can be increased all the way up to 90% based on your performance.
                            a(href="#").button.button--gradient-border.button--small.border-gradient
                                .button__text Learn More
    section.section.section--rewards.js-inview
        .container.container--inner-top
            .rewards-block
                .steps-block__top-title
                    .title.title--border-mini
                        span Step Two
                .rewards-block__top
                    h2.title.title--section
                        | Customize Your
                        span.default-gradient  Plan
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                        | We appreciate that every trader and trading style is different. With that in mind we offer the opportunity to customise your trading accounts at the checkout.
                .rewards-block__list
                    .model-item
                        .model-item__body
                            .model-item__icon
                                img(src='content/images/empty.gif' class="lazy" data-src="content/images/icons/infinite.svg" width="124" height="62" alt="infinite")
                            .model-item__sub
                                | Unlimited
                                span.default-gradient  Days
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                                | Trade at your own pace with complete freedom and flexibility, so that you can focus on your performance and profit target.
                    .model-item.model-item--shadow
                        .model-item__body
                            .model-item__icon
                                img(src='content/images/empty.gif' class="lazy" data-src="content/images/icons/percent2.svg" width="86" height="86" alt="infinite")
                            .model-item__sub
                                | Extra 15%
                                span.default-gradient   Profit Split
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                                | RMaximize your earning potential and increase your profit split by 15%. Trades who upgrade their profit split will receive a 90% profit split.
                    .model-item
                        .model-item__body
                            .model-item__icon
                                img(src='content/images/empty.gif' class="lazy" data-src="content/images/icons/wallet.svg" width="102" height="84" alt="infinite")
                            .model-item__sub
                                | Bi-weekly
                                span.default-gradient  Payouts
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                                | Our bi-weekly payout system ensures that you receive your earnings on a regular basis, without having to wait for long periods.
    section.section.section--rewards.js-inview
        .container.container--inner-top
            .rewards-block.rewards-block--secondary
                .steps-block__top-title
                    .title.title--border-mini
                        span Step Three
                .rewards-block__top
                    h2.title.title--section
                        | Evaluation
                        span.default-gradient  Process
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                        | The evaluation process involves simple assessments to understand a trader’s ability to generate profitable trades through a combination of technical expertise, discipline and risk management skills.
                .rewards-block__list-two
                    .process-item
                        .process-item__body
                            .title.title--section.title--white 01.
                            .process-item__title Assessment
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger-two
                                | From 0 to funded in 1 simple step.
                                | Generate a return of at 10% on your trading assessment within 30days (or upgrade to unlimited days at the checkout) without incurring losses that exceed a a maximum trailing drawdown of 6%.
                                | After successfully reaching a 10% profit target traders will then be given access to funded trading capital.
                    .process-item
                        .process-item__body
                            .title.title--section.title--white 02.
                            .process-item__title Verification
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger-two
                                | Following the assessment, the second step of the evaluation process progresses to the Verification stage.
                                | Upon successful completion of the verification stage, you will earn the title of a certified FXIFY trader.
                    .process-item
                        .process-item__body
                            .title.title--section.title--white 03.
                            .process-item__title You’re Funded
                            .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger-two
                                p As a FXIFY certified trader, you can earn up to 90% of your profits by showing discipline, focus, and consistent profitability.
                                p Consistent profitability can also lead to scaling opportunities and increased trading capital.
                                p Join our community of successful traders and discover your true potential with FXIFY.
    section.section.section--dewards.js-inview
        .dewards-block
            .container.container--inner-top
                .dewards-block__top
                    h2.title.title--section
                        | Withdrawal On
                        span.default-gradient  Demand
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                        | Traders have the opportunity to receive up to 90% of the profits earned on their funded account and can easily withdraw their earnings.
            .dewards-block__list
                .dewards-item
                    .dewards-item__title Up to 90% profit
                    .dewards-item__mid
                        span
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger
                        | Traders can receive up to 90% profit split on their live accounts.
                .dewards-item
                    .dewards-item__title Easy
                    .dewards-item__mid
                        span
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger
                        | Experience an easy and seamless withdrawal process.
                .dewards-item
                    .dewards-item__title Flexible
                    .dewards-item__mid
                        span
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger
                        | There are up to 15 different payout options to choose from.
                .dewards-item
                    .dewards-item__title On Demand
                    .dewards-item__mid
                        span
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--bigger
                        | Traders can withdraw their profits on demand for their first payout.
