    section.section.section--experience.js-inview
        .container
            .experience-block
                .experience-block__top
                    h2.title.title--section
                        | Join Our Team Of
                        span.default-gradient  Experienced Traders
                    .simple-text.simple-text--white.simple-text--medium
                        | Traders can take their trading to the next level and embark on their journey to become funded prop traders. Choose between a Evaluation and Express account and customize it to suit their trading strategy.
